---
import Icon from '../icon-sprite';
import { Logo, Logos } from '../utilities/logo';
---

<section
  id="shv-section"
  class="flex flex-col md:grid md:grid-cols-[40%_1fr] py-10 border-y-2 max-h-screen"
>
  <div class="md:sticky md:top-48 md:self-start">
    <div class="px-8 border-l border-muted-foreground/30 flex flex-col">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <h1 class="font-mono font-bold md:text-3xl text-muted-foreground">SHV</h1>
        <Logo name={Logos.SHV} className="h-4 w-6" />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground/80 uppercase font-mono mt-1"
      >
        <Icon name="pinCircle" className="size-3.5" />
        <p class="font-medium text-muted-foreground/80">Palo Alto, 2025-</p>
      </div>
      <p class="font-medium text-muted-foreground/80 mt-2">Software Engineer // Internal Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="px-8 mt-4 text-muted-foreground/80 flex flex-col gap-2">
      <p>
        Sutter Hill Ventures is a quiet powerhouse of Silicon Valley, and employs an internal team
        of around 10 engineers to (1) explore the frontier of technology and (2) build products with
        portfolio companies.
      </p>
      <p>
        Many of my experiments have been with <a
          href="https://www.modelcontextprotocol.org"
          class="underline">Model Context Protocol</a
        >, a framework for adding context to language models. Such projects include:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside pl-4">
        <li>
          <a href="https://agentdb.dev" class="underline">AgentDB</a>
          <Icon name="arrowUpRight" className="inline mb-1 size-4" />
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://chatdb.io" class="underline">ChatDB</a>
          <Icon name="arrowUpRight" className="inline mb-1 size-4" />
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Additionally, I've had the privilege of building with the following portfolio companies:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside pl-4">
        <li>
          <a href="https://ridgebio.com" class="underline">Ridge Biosciences</a>
          <Icon name="arrowUpRight" className="inline mb-1 size-4" />
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://integratedbiosciences.com" class="underline">Integrated Biosciences</a>
          <Icon name="arrowUpRight" className="inline mb-1 size-4" />
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://run.so" class="underline">Run</a>
          <Icon name="arrowUpRight" className="inline mb-1 size-4" />
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://arianetworks.com" class="underline">Aria Networks</a>
          <Icon name="arrowUpRight" className="inline mb-1 size-4" />
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hidden md:block h-auto">
    <img src="/images/chatdb.webp" alt="SHV" />
  </div>
</section>
